usage: git stow [<options>]

Stow branches and tags

    -h|--help               display help
    -r|--recursive          traverse submodules recursively
    -p|--push               mirror tags when done
                            WARNING: remote tags are deleted and replaced with local tags

1. Remove already classified branches
2. Remove already promoted vbranches
3. Classify branches
   - archive old branches (> 1 year)
4. Remove already classified tags
5. Remove already promoted vtags
6. Classify tags
   - archive old tags (> 1 year)
   - remove vtags prerelease leading zeros
7. Promote vtags
   - move vtags in associated vbranch folder
8. Process orphan vtags

example:
    git stow
    git stow --push